text: Pranayamazha is a 1999 Indian Malayalam film, directed by Nithin Kumar, starring Manoj K Jayan and Priya Raman in the lead role. ==Cast== * Manoj K Jayan * Thilakan * Murali * Siddique * Sathar * Chandni * Jagadish * Kaveri * Manuraj * Meena Ganesh * Ponnamma Babu * Priya Raman * Reena * Sarath Haridas * TS Raju ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 films Category:Indian films Category:1990s Malayalam-language films
title: Pranayamazha
